{"tid":1689063,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"6點至7點嘅堅尼地道近麥當勞道一帶有冇人知咩事","createTime":"2019-11-02T16:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T03:56:16.000Z","uid":148795,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7909729f52c16dcc0a83d1064cd8a74812a197","tid":1689063,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:15:21.000Z","msg":"唔想喺標題打 救人 兩隻字一陣又話標題黨<br />\n但係有冇手足發夢係6點至7點左右喺堅尼地道出返嚟<br />\n我有個fd6點8左右諗住有麥當勞道入堅尼地道<br />\n大概係呢個位<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XosCNFT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXosCNFT.jpg&h=8886f250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後班狗封撚左話唔比上山<br />\n有隻狗話啱啱掃完一班黑衣人<br />\n想問有冇手足係大概呢個時間喺堅尼地道成功逃出<br />\n好怕有堆手足比人捉左都冇人知<br />\n求下大家幫推"},{"pid":"a83225b8d2c14dfa0dec38f32db6ddfa7cc61f64","tid":1689063,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"推 救人"},{"pid":"7ede6af8a0307d35c3af03368a462118ef0837bf","tid":1689063,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"有冇人嗰陣發夢係現場"},{"pid":"33bd03c5f1fa99a787cb7c8f36f7b5965a5dbedf","tid":1689063,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:17:03.000Z","msg":"求下大家"},{"pid":"d6d8133a039cfd8f1877803be794a5eb5db2d0d9","tid":1689063,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"我唔想做標題黨啊唔好逼我啦"},{"pid":"5cde4696a5b5cf238b4e7fddae2013ee962d1e38","tid":1689063,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:17:52.000Z","msg":"救人啊連登仔<br />\n我見出面好多po有手足話行過堅尼地道架"},{"pid":"2a75bb4a40611e0dd15f4d149fda61acb7f792d2","tid":1689063,"uid":148795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"到底有冇手足比狗咬"},{"pid":"83afa9dfb8cdc2b680eb6327bc2050d888e455e9","tid":1689063,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:18:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid"